---
description: SvelteKit routes and data loading
globs: src/routes/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Route data must use `+page.ts` `load()` and `await parent()` for `ds` — see CLAUDE.md § Data loading.

Do not use `onMount` to fetch entity data for pages.

Canonical entity URLs: `/entity/[entityId]`. Typed `/tablets/[id]` routes only redirect.
